<!--
  template_jasia.tmx — Jasias Quest comprehensive map template
  Based on template.tmx (jasias-quest fork of Andor's Trail)

  LAYER STACK ORDER
  ─────────────────
  Ground            tile layer  — base floor art
  Ground_replace    tile layer  — blank; swap in above Ground for Replace_newyears
  Objects           tile layer  — objects / furniture art
  Objects_replace   tile layer  — blank; swap in above Objects for Replace_newyears
  Above             tile layer  — overhead / fringe art
  Above_replace     tile layer  — blank; swap in above Above for Replace_newyears
  Walkable          tile layer  — collision / passability
  Mapevents         object layer — exits N/S/E/W spanning full map sides
  Spawn_animals     object layer — beach terrain animals, whole map
  Spawn_faction     object layer — human faction NPCs
  Keys_door         object layer — locked door with key / lockpick / bash
  Keys_forage       object layer — example foraging spots
  Keys_crafting     object layer — all crafting stations
  Keys_mining       object layer — all mining vein tiers
  Replace_newyears  object layer — New Year holiday event trigger + layer swap
  Spawn_replace     object layer — New Years Baby NPC spawn

  SEE: README_template_jasia.md for full reference
-->
